{
  "texts": [
    "Electronic informed survey consent was collected, and verbal informed consent for interviews was noted.",
    "All participants provided their consent willingly and were told they could leave without penalty.",
    "Data collected from study participants was treated under absolute confidentiality measures.",
    "No identifying information was collected, and each participant received a unique code.",
    "Participant responses were saved as an encrypted file to which the researcher was the only one with access."
  ]
}